      "content": "that \"leap\" you're talking about... it doesn't feel like something i can just walk into. it feels more like there's no path back to being human again. when the respect is gone and the name is ruined, you're just a burden to everyone around you. it feels more logical to just stop fighting the current, you know? like, if the person i was is dead, why am i still here pretending?",
